msgctxt "1692"
msgid "Akiyama"
msgstr "Akiyama"

msgctxt "1696"
msgid "Energetic Foreigner"
msgstr "Extranjero enérgico"

msgctxt "1700"
msgid "Talk_Quest"
msgstr "Talk_Quest"

msgctxt "56_Akiyama"
msgid "(Better start looking for leads on Midorikawa.)"
msgstr "(Será mejor que busque pistas de ese Midorikawa)."

msgctxt "68_Energetic Foreigner"
msgid "Man, oh man! The perfect shot's so close I can almost smell it! Or did I forget to wear deodorant?"
msgstr "¡Santo cielo! ¡La toma perfecta está tan cerca que puedo olerla! ¿O se me olvidó echarme desodorante?"

msgctxt "92_Energetic Foreigner"
msgid "You there! Did you see those tough dudes flashin' their muscles like it's nobody's business? Nothing quite as dangerous as a thug with something to prove."
msgstr "¡Tú! ¿Viste a esos tipos sacando a relucir sus músculos? No hay nada más peligroso que un matón queriendo demostrar algo."

msgctxt "104_Energetic Foreigner"
msgid "But hey, that's what Kamurocho's all about! The glitz, the glamor, the gigantic guys shaking down passersby! Not that I <Italic>like<Italic> that last part."
msgstr "¡Pero bueno, así es Kamurocho! El ocio, el glamour, los fortachones intimidando a los civiles. Bueno, no me gusta eso último."

msgctxt "116_Akiyama"
msgid "(\"Tough dudes\"? Maybe he's talking about Midorikawa.)"
msgstr "(¿Fortachones? Tal vez se refiera a Midorikawa)."

msgctxt "128_Akiyama"
msgid "Hold on there, buddy! Think we can talk for a sec?"
msgstr "Oye, ¿tienes un momento para hablar?"

